## Evolution Log 格式

`_bmad/_memory/evolution-log-R{N}.md`

```yaml
round: N
team_config: sprint-mode   # solo / sprint / parallel-sprint
teammate_count: 8

completed_stories:
  - { id: FE-1, status: done }

blocking_log:
  - from: dev-frontend-1
    waiting_on: dev-backend-1
    issue: "/api/login error response schema 未定义"
    wait_time: 2h
    root_cause: "API 契约未在规划阶段锁定"

tension_points:
  # TTL 规则：initial_ttl: 2 | 每轮 ttl_decrement: 1 | ttl_remaining: 0 时下轮开始前必须决策
  - id: T-1
    description: "状态管理方案：Zustand vs Jotai"
    status: UNRESOLVED
    ttl_remaining: 1       # 归零时：decision_required_at: 0，强制决策后才能启动下轮团队

next_round_suggestions:
  - "规划阶段增加 architect-frontend，提前锁定前端技术决策"
  - "Story 依赖调整：BE-1 应早于 FE-1 启动"

next_team_config: sprint-mode
```

